      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi I’m a beginner at this, and whenever I try to connect the webhook URL from my slack workflow I’ get an error message that says Failed to communicate with URL provided.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/d90ed0da77c05d614fb671ad9f8c38b088d3bd1c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/d90ed0da77c05d614fb671ad9f8c38b088d3bd1c_2_690x424.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"424\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">915×563 30.2 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\nI do get the challenge token in slack after clicking connect but as it appears so, I am unable to return the challenge to Monday.<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/c/c2e60ae7ed9b4d5f38d66f7570e7d9380ce19626.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"544\" height=\"201\" /><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/5/569e1e866dfc3ff17f1afd2d1b2b930fc91411c4.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/5/569e1e866dfc3ff17f1afd2d1b2b930fc91411c4_2_412x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"412\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">505×612 32.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Can anyone help me please? What am I doing wrong?  <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
